{% doc %}
  @prompt
    crea una seccion de acuerdo a lo siguiente: UNCHAINED OFFICE COFFEE PROGRAM — FINAL VERSION
    Short Subtitle
    
    Coffee that fuels your team.
    And frees the people who grow it.
    
    Short Description (Top Section)
    
    Transform your workplace coffee into a benefit with real impact.
    The Unchained Office Coffee Program brings freshly roasted specialty coffee to your team—powered by a professional Eversys superautomatic machine, included in your plan—while sending 70% of all coffee revenue directly to small Colombian growers.
    
    It’s a unique opportunity for your office to enjoy café-level quality and transparency normally only found in specialty coffee shops.
    Now available at work.
    Now changing the chain.
    
    Why Bring Unchained to Your Office?
    
    Eversys machine included – A world-class superautomatic espresso system delivering barista-quality drinks at the push of a button.
    
    70% of revenue goes directly to farmers – A radically fair model that shifts value back to the people who grow your coffee.
    
    Specialty coffee, every day – Fresh-roasted microlots delivered automatically based on your consumption.
    
    Unique access to premium coffee at work – True specialty coffee without leaving the building.
    
    Operational simplicity – Clean setups, simple workflows, high performance.
    
    Team culture that actually works – Coffee becomes a shared ritual, not just caffeine.
    
    How It Works
    1 — We install your Eversys machine
    
    Your plan includes a premium Eversys superautomatic machine, configured for your space and calibrated for Unchained coffees.
    
    2 — Choose your plan size
    
    Designed around your headcount and preferred consumption style.
    
    3 — Fresh roasted coffee on a fixed schedule
    
    We roast and deliver automatically so your office never runs out.
    
    4 — Transparent impact
    
    Track how your program sends 70% of revenue back to small producers, improving livelihoods and building long-term resilience in Colombian coffee communities.
    
    Plan Options
    Startup Fuel (Up to ~20 people)
    
    1 Eversys superautomatic machine 
{% enddoc %}
